### 5. **Image Model File Types (ImageModelV3File)**

**Location:** `/packages/provider/src/image-model/v3/image-model-v3-file.ts`

Supports both URL and base64/binary data:
```typescript
export type ImageModelV3File =
  | {
      type: 'file';
      mediaType: string;
      data: string | Uint8Array;
